headline.main: In Season Openers, the Red Bulls Rally and New York City F.C. Falls Short
headline.print_headline: Red Bulls Rally to Win Season Opener

lead_paragraph: South Korea's military said on Monday there was a low chance that four North Korean missiles launched earlier in the day were intercontinental ballistic missiles (ICBMs), but more time would be needed to confirm.
